## Benchmarking Workflow

- [ ] 1. Define benchmarks: Identify relevant industry standards and competitive reference points
- [ ] 2. Gather data: Collect client performance data and industry benchmark data
- [ ] 3. Compare metrics: Align metrics on a like-for-like basis (CPM, CTR, CPA, ROAS, etc.)
- [ ] 4. Gap analysis: Identify where performance is above or below benchmark
- [ ] 5. Contextualize: Consider seasonality, market conditions, and audience differences
- [ ] 6. Recommend: Identify quick wins and longer-term improvements

## Key Inputs
- Client: {{client_name}}
- Industry: {{industry}}
- Metrics to benchmark: {{metrics}}
- Reference period: {{reference_period}}
